Creates an object of class QFeatures from an object of class MSnSet

convertMSnset2QFeatures.Rd

xxxx

convertMSnset2QFeatures(
  obj,
  analysis,
  parentProtId,
  keyId,
  pipelineType = NULL,
  processes = NULL
)

Arguments

obj

xxx.
analysis

xxx
parentProtId

For peptide entities, a string which is the name of a column in rowData. It contains the id of parent proteins and is used to generate adjacency matrix and process to aggregation.
keyId

The indice of the column containing the ID of entities (peptides or proteins)
pipelineType

xxxx
processes

xxxx

Value

An instance of class QFeatures.

Author

Samuel Wieczorek

library(MSnbase)
